         ENTERED=20040511
         UPDATED=20040511
           SHORT="A key-grabbing tool."
cat << EOF
bbkeys is the keygrabber for the *box window managers. bbkeys handles all keybindings and keyboard shortcuts. It uses Blackbox's Image classes for rendering its look and feel, so bbkeys will draw itself to match whatever style is used. It is highly configurable via the bbconf GUI utility, the included bbkeysconf.pl perl script, or via hand-editing bbkeys's config file.
EOF

